xpeppers.interview.strategy

Class Rates

  • java.lang.Object
    • xpeppers.interview.strategy.Rates

  • public final class Rates
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used as a provider of rates for the tax strategies. All the rates should be coded here instead of the Strategy classes. This approach adds a layer of independence.
